!! [[0.9.0|https://crosseye.github.io/TW5-JSON_Convert/0.9.0/]]
//Released 2026-05-15//

Documentation, plugin transforms, and naming polish.

* Documentation pass: README, Overview tiddler, plugin usage / license tiddlers, LICENSE
* Convert-braces icon and favicon; PageControls icon and button
* Plugin-shipped wikitext transforms: ''to-upper-case'', ''to-lower-case'', ''to-title-case'', ''slugify''
* Rename ''mapping profile'' → ''profile'' throughout (incl. tag `$:/tags/json-convert/mapping` → `…/profile`)
* Rename ''split-csv'' → ''split-commas''; add ''split-to-titles''
* Fix: `slugify` now uses search-replace (not regsub); shadow tiddlers load in transform / picker filters so plugin-shipped wikitext transforms actually work
* Staging bulk buttons prefixed with `Set all to:` for clarity
